 Actress cum physiotherapist, Jemima Osunde shared on Twitter how advising such people is a complete waste of time and effort as they will not yield. Adesua Etomi whom Osunde shares a really close relationship did not let the tweet pass without a not-so-subtle shade at its author. She revealed that based on past experiences, the younger woman just dragged herself with her tweet.Information Nigeria recalls Adesua Etomi, amongst other celebrities recently expressed concern over the state of the nation based on the recent Kaduna/Abuja train attacks.